Microsoft Azure Management Libraries for Java 2.0.0-SNAPSHOT

Packages 
Package Description
com.microsoft.azure.v2.management
This package contains the Azure rollup client.
com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.compute
This package contains the classes for ComputeManagementClient.
com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.graphrbac
This package contains the classes for GraphRbacManagementClient.
com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.msi
This package contains the classes for ManagedServiceIdentityClient.
com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.network
This package contains the classes for NetworkManagementClient.
com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.network.model
This package contains the common interfaces for resource models in networking.
com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.resources
This package contains the classes for PolicyClient.
com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.resources.fluentcore.arm
This package contains the common resource manager utility classes that are useful to other management plane libraries.
com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.resources.fluentcore.arm.collection
This package contains the base class for resource collections.
com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.resources.fluentcore.arm.models
This package contains the base classes for resource models.
com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.resources.fluentcore.collection
This package contains the base class for resource collections.
com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.resources.fluentcore.dag
This package contains the graph related classes that are useful for performing cloud requests in parallel.
com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.resources.fluentcore.model
This package contains the base classes for resource models, and their variants for creating and updating scenarios.
com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.storage
This package contains the classes for StorageManagementClient.
com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.trafficmanager
This package contains the classes for TrafficManagerManagementClient.
